    "In combination with CNN, transfer learning and ensemble learning also support the analysis of X-rays.",
    "CT scans are used for diagnosis in ML and its sub-fields; however, they are less recommended than X-rays since an X-ray is adequate for diagnosing pneumonia.Employing CNNs to analyze CT images successfully identifies and categorizes lung nodules, which are minor growths that may signify lung cancer.",
    "CNNs can be trained on massive CT scan data to learn the features associated with various lung nodules, allowing for reliable identification and classification.",
    "CNN has been used in many studies to accurately identify lung nodules, making it a viable technique for the early identification of lung cancer.",
    "Conventional ML is preferred in tandem with CT scans as well."
